('44631','15846','5','Unique villa with separate guest house and tennis court in Cas Catala'),
('44632','15847','5','This 4,000 m² property is located in the exclusive, upmarket Bendinat area – just a 20 minutes drive away from the airport, 10 minutes from the bustling city of Palma, and just 5 minutes from the exclusive marina of Puerto Portals. The property is set on the hills of Cas Catala Nou and has been finished to a very high standard using only the best materials. There are three separate living units on the property, which is surrounded by a 120 metres long, elegant  wall made of polished stone. The 8-person stainless steel, glass-fronted lift will take you from the ground floor to the living area or further up to the penthouse terrace with spectacular views over the Bay of Palma.\r\nThe estate comprises of  the main house and the separate guesthouse. The property also includes a large number of utility rooms such as a fully equipped laundry, fully equipped caretaker facilities with modern tools, several water tanks, own water supply with special water treatment room, as well as several storage rooms. Recently there has been installed an independent internal power supply system for heating and electricity.\r\nMain house\r\nGround floor: There are 2 separate underground garages for up to 9 cars.\r\nFirst floor: staff apartment - comprising of a spacious living room (approx. 40 m²) with access to the patio, kitchen with dining area, two bedrooms, bathroom and office room.\r\nSecond floor: guest apartment – with living room leading to a terrace, bar-kitchen and dining area, bedroom, and spacious marble bathroom.\r\nThird and fourth floor: master apartment - spacious living room with dining area for eight people (5-metre-high ceiling), open terrace offering breathtaking views, ceiling-high glass sliding-door system leading to the swimming pool that is located next to the living room for indoor and outdoor living. A library with office area, kitchen with terrace, a children’s suite comprising of a large bedroom with terrace, a small bedroom/fitness room and marble bathroom.\r\nFifth floor: penthouse - is home to the master bedroom with separate lift access, dressing area, and marble bathroom, small kitchen pantry, as well as additional living room offering magnificent views. The penthouse terrace is approx. 80 m² and boasts electrically controlled vertical and horizontal sun protection. \r\nThe separate guesthouse  has its own access and covered parking space. It disposes of three spacious bedrooms, three bathrooms, a magnificent, spacious living room overlooking the Bay of Palma, a kitchen, vestibule with small office, and two terraces. The guesthouse boasts an elegant design, like an old English yacht club.\r\nThe outside area and installations are of highest quality, there are beautifully landscaped gardens with irrigation system.  There are numerous sun-protected terraces, a large swimming pool with 3-metre diving platform, a magnificent waterfall that connects the large 3-metre-deep pool with the heated pool next to the living room. Furthermore, there is tennis court sheltered from the wind by high cypress trees.\r\nThe property is also for rent for 15,000 EUR monthly (no commission!).'),
